sentences: Shannon Arrum Williams (born 26 May 1998), known professionally as Shannon, is a British-South Korean singer, actress, twitch streamer and voice actress based in South Korea.
She officially debuted as a solo artist in December 2014 with her digital single, Daybreak Rain.
